javac.nio

接口 PathFileManager

  • 所有超级接口:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, javax.tools.JavaFileManager, javax.tools.OptionChecker
    所有已知实现类:
    JavacPathFileManager

    public interface PathFileManager
extends javax.tools.JavaFileManager
    File manager based on Path. Eventually, this should be moved to javax.tools. Also, JavaCompiler might reasonably provide a method getPathFileManager, similar to getStandardFileManager. However, would need to be handled carefully as another forward reference from langtools to jdk.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

    • 方法详细资料

      • getDefaultFileSystem

        java.nio.file.FileSystem getDefaultFileSystem()
        Get the default file system used to create paths. If no value has been set, the default file system is FileSystems.getDefault().

      • setDefaultFileSystem

        void setDefaultFileSystem(java.nio.file.FileSystem fs)
        Set the default file system used to create paths.
        参数:
        fs - the default file system used to create any new paths.

      • getJavaFileObjectsFromPaths

        java.lang.Iterable<? extends javax.tools.JavaFileObject> getJavaFileObjectsFromPaths(java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.nio.file.Path> paths)
        Get file objects representing the given files.
        参数:
        paths - a list of paths
        返回:
        a list of file objects
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the list of paths includes a directory

      • getJavaFileObjects

        java.lang.Iterable<? extends javax.tools.JavaFileObject> getJavaFileObjects(java.nio.file.Path... paths)
        Get file objects representing the given paths. Convenience method equivalent to: 
             getJavaFileObjectsFromPaths(Arrays.asList(paths))
        参数:
        paths - an array of paths
        返回:
        a list of file objects
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the array of files includes a directory
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the given array contains null elements

      • getPath

        java.nio.file.Path getPath(javax.tools.FileObject fo)
        Return the Path for a file object that has been obtained from this file manager.
        参数:
        fo - A file object that has been obtained from this file manager.
        返回:
        The underlying Path object.
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - is the file object was not obtained from from this file manager.

      • getLocation

        java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.nio.file.Path> getLocation(javax.tools.JavaFileManager.Location location)
        Get the search path associated with the given location.
        参数:
        location - a location
        返回:
        a list of paths or null if this location has no associated search path
        另请参阅:
        setLocation(javax.tools.JavaFileManager.Location, java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.nio.file.Path>)

      • setLocation

        void setLocation(javax.tools.JavaFileManager.Location location,
                 java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.nio.file.Path> searchPath)
          throws java.io.IOException
        Associate the given search path with the given location. Any previous value will be discarded.
        参数:
        location - a location
        searchPath - a list of files, if null use the default search path for this location
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if location is an output location and searchpath does not contain exactly one element
        java.io.IOException - if location is an output location and searchpath does not represent an existing directory
        另请参阅:
        getLocation(javax.tools.JavaFileManager.Location)
